JFiles.Constants

Interface XO


  • public interface XO
    Constants related to XO game
    X, O, BLANK - game filed constants - cross, zero, nothing
    FIELD_SIZE, WIN_LINE_SIZE - Size of game field, Qty of X or O in a row to win game
    WIN, LOOSE, EVEN - ids of game result
